	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hein?!<delay20 /> Comment ça?<delay20 /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Il faut pas
