	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Sans rire, t'es aussi un<gender2 m="" f="e" /> Chevelu<gender2 m="" f="e" />,
